@QA_Backend_BaseUrl = http://localhost:5056

### Health check
GET {{QA_Backend_BaseUrl}}/api/health

### Ask question
POST {{QA_Backend_BaseUrl}}/api/questions/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the refund policy?"
}

### Knowledge base status
GET {{QA_Backend_BaseUrl}}/api/knowledge/status

### Reload knowledge base
POST {{QA_Backend_BaseUrl}}/api/knowledge/reload
